Scrabble challenge

*Objective: Input a string containing the word that needs to be scored based on the assigned points per letter*

Steps required to complete task

#1 Declare an object that shows all letters and their assigned numerical values.

#2 Create a guard function that will return the value '0' when input is null/not a previously stated character.

#3 Create a variable that will contain the declared word and;
   -put all characters in lower case
   -divide it into an array.

#4 Use forEach to assign a numerical value to each declared letter in the array. (guard function will return 0 if character is not in previously stated object)

#5 Add numbers in array and return total.